Your max fee must be higher than the sum of the base fee and the tip in order for your transaction to be processed.

If there is a difference between the max fee and other fees (base fee + tip) it will be refunded.
#nfts #NFT #Ethereum #ETH

A tip is a priority fee that is used to incentivize the miners who do the work of processing your transaction. 

You can increase the tip to have your transaction prioritized.

It is also possible to designate a max fee.

#nfts #NFT #Ethereum #ETH

The base fee is the minimum amount you must pay for your transaction to be included in the next block. (A block is a list of ordered records that stores data on the blockchain.)

The base fee is automatically calculated by the demand for previous blocks.
#nfts #NFT #Ethereum #ETH

Max fee, base fee, and tip are the three amounts that determine the cost of your gas.

In order to have your transaction recorded onto the Ethereum blockchain, you are required to pay a base fee.
